jcr:content.jcr:title: GIRLtopia Journey - Stark Museum of Art

data.details: The Stark Museum of Art in Orange is hosting the Women, Art, and Social Change travelling exhibit from the Smithsonian, and this innovative exhibit is the theme and backdrop for this Senior GIRLtopia Journey. Explore in a day-long program how women have impacted the art world and how you can make an impact in your world! Girls will have the chance to create a personal piece of art alongside certified personnel as well as hear from successful women.
